erfly)''||''Aglais urticae'' || [[File:Aglais urticae LC0310.jpg|150px]] ||<ref name=naturDK/>\n|-\n|{{EGY}} || [[Steppe eagle]] ||''Aquila nipalensis'' || [[File:Steppe Eagle's Gape.jpg|150px]] ||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://voices.nationalgeographic.com/2012/04/27/top-25-wild-bird-photographs-of-the-week-11/majestic-steppe-eagle-india-rohit-singh/|title=Majestic steppe eagle photographed in India. They are the national animal of Egypt.|work=nationalgeographic.com|access-date=2015-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617062708/http://voices.nationalgeographic.com/2012/04/27/top-25-wild-bird-photographs-of-the-week-11/majestic-steppe-eagle-india-rohit-singh/|archive-date=2015-06-17|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{EST}} || [[Wolf]] ||''Canis lupus'' ||[[File:European grey wolf in Prague zoo.jpg|150px]] ||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.postimees.ee/4477987/wolf-picked-national-animal-over-hedgehog|title=Wolf picked national animal over hedgehog}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{ERI}} || [[Arabian camel]] ||''Camelus dromedarius'' || [[File:Camelus dromedarius on Sinai.jpg|150px]] ||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldatlas.com/webimage/countrys/africa/eritrea/ersymbols.htm |title=Eritrea State Symbols, Song, Flags, and More |publisher=worldatlas.com|accessdate=2017-12-01}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{ETH}} || [[Lion]] ||''Panthera leo'' || [[File:Lion waiting in Namibia.jpg|150px]] ||<ref name=\"Good\"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldatlas.com/webimage/countrys/africa/ethiopia/etsymbols.htm |title=Ethiopia State Symbols, Song, Flag, and More |publisher=worldatlas.com|accessdate=2013-03-21}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{FRO}} || [[Eurasian oystercatcher]] ''(national bird)''||''Haematopus ostralgus'' ||[[File:Haematopus ostralegus Norway.jpg|150px]] ||<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.visitfaroeislands.com/Default.aspx?ID=10008 |title=Get an impression |publisher=visitfaroeislands.com/ |accessdate=2013-03-21 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130721014643/http://www.visitfaroeislands.com/Default.aspx?ID=10008 |archivedate=21 July 2013 }}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" |{{FIN}} || [[Brown bear]] ''(national animal)''||''Ursus arctos'' ||[[File:European Brown Bear.jpg|150px]] ||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://yle.fi/aihe/artikkeli/2010/09/16/karhu-suomen-kansalliselain |title=Karhu on Suomen kansallisel\u00e4in |publisher=yle.fi |language=fi |accessdate=2018-03-03}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Whooper swan]] ''(national bird)''||''Cygnus cygnus'' || [[File:Whooper Swan (Cygnus cygnus) (26).jpg|150px]] ||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://yle.fi/aihe/artikkeli/2012/07/07/laulujoutsen-kansallislintu |title=Laulujoutsen, kansallislintu |publisher=yle.fi |language=fi |accessdate=2018-03-03\n}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Holly blue]] ''(national butterfly)''||''Celastrina argiolus'' || [[File:Celastrina argiolus1.jpg|150px]] ||<ref>{{cite web |url=https://suomifinland100.fi/finlands-national-butterfly-is-the-holly-blue/?lang=en |title=Finland's national butterfly is the holly blue |website=suomifinland100.fi |accessdate=2018-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180619140728/https://suomifinland100.fi/finlands-national-butterfly-is-the-holly-blue/?lang=en |archive-date=19 June 2018 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|-\n|[[European perch]] ''(national fish)''||''Perca fluviatilis'' || [[File:Perca fluviatilis.jpg|150px]] ||<ref name=\"this-is-finland\">{{cite web |url=https://finland.fi/life-society/iconic-finnish-nature-symbols-stand-out/ |title=Iconic Finnish nature symbols stand out |website=This is Finland |publisher=Finland Promotion Board |accessdate=2018-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171025235927/https://finland.fi/life-society/iconic-finnish-nature-symbols-stand-out/ |archive-date=25 October 2017 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Coccinella septempunctata|Seven-spot ladybird]] ''(national insect)''||''Coccinella septempunctata'' || [[File:Leppis404.JPG|150px]] ||<ref name=\"this-is-finland\"/>\n|-\n|{{FRA}}\n|[[Gallic rooster]]\n|''Gallus gallus domesticus''\n|[[File:Coq-gaulois-dore.JPG|frameless|150x150px]]\n|<ref>{{Cite web|title = Le coq|url = http://www.elysee.fr/la-presidence/le-coq/|website = www.elysee.fr|accessdate = 2015-11-29|language = fr-FR}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{GAB}} || [[Black panther]] ||''Panthera pardus'' || [[File:Blackleopard.JPG|150px]] || <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://einfon.com/nationalsymbols/national-animal-of-gabon/|title=National Animal of Gabon|date=2 May 2017|access-date=2018-09-08|language=en-US}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{GMB}}<!--Gambia--> || [[Lion]] || ''Panthera leo'' || [[File:Lion d'Afrique.jpg|150px]] ||<ref name=\"BioSci\"/>\n|-\n|{{GER}}||[[Coat of arms of Germany|Bundesadler]] ''(heraldic \"Federal Eagle\")''||style=\"background:#ccc;\" |'''Mythical'''||[[File:Coat of arms of Germany.svg|150px]]||<ref name=\"BioSci\"/><ref>{{Cite web|title = German Symbols|url = http://www.worldatlas.com/webimage/countrys/europe/germany/desymbols.htm/|website = www.worldatlas.com|accessdate = 2017-08-11|language = en-EN}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{GRE}}||[[Dolphin]] (national animal) || ''[[Common dolphin|Delphinus]]'' || [[File:Delfine im Golf von Korinth, Griechenland.jpg|150px]]||<ref name=worldatlas>{{cite web|website=worldatlas|url=http://www.worldatlas.com/webimage/countrys/europe/greece/grsymbols.htm|title=Greek Symbols}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{GUA}} || [[Quetzal]] ||''Pharomachrus mocinno'' ||[[File:Quetzal01.jpg|150px]] ||<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.conap.gob.gt/index.php/servicios-en-linea/noticias/83-celebraciones/331-dia-del-quetzal.html |title=D\u00eda del quetzal |publisher=conap.gob.gt |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310205709/http://conap.gob.gt/index.php/servicios-en-linea/noticias/83-celebraciones/331-dia-del-quetzal.html |archivedate=10 March 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flag|Haiti}}\n|[[Hispaniolan trogon|Hispaniolan Trogan]] \n|''Priotelus roseigaster''\n|[[File:Hispaniolan Trogon (Priotelus roseigaster) (8082799519).jpg|150px]]\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cia.gov/library/public