 Pheasants |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070112033104/http://www.gbwf.org/pheasants/monal.html#images |archivedate=12 January 2007 }}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | {{NED}} || [[Lion (heraldry)|Lion]] ''(heraldic symbol)''||''Panthera leo'' ||[[File:Royal Coat of Arms of the Netherlands.svg|150px]] || <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.koninklijkhuis.nl/globale-paginas/taalrubrieken/english/monarchy/coat-of-arms-and-standard/ |title=Dutch coat of arms and standard |accessdate=2012-11-10 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121230114541/http://www.koninklijkhuis.nl/globale-paginas/taalrubrieken/english/monarchy/coat-of-arms-and-standard |archivedate=30 December 2012 }}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Black-tailed godwit]] ''(national bird)'' ||''Limosa limosa'' || [[File:Limosa limosa (Uitkerke).jpg|150px]] || <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nu.nl/dieren/4166987/grutto-verkozen-nationale-vogel.html | title=Grutto verkozen tot nationale vogel | accessdate=2016-05-31}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{NZL}} || [[Kiwi]]||''Apteryx'' sp. ||[[File:TeTuatahianui.jpg|150px]] ||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.teara.govt.nz/en/government-and-nation/9 |title=Teara.govt.nz |publisher=Teara.govt.nz |date=22 September 2012 |accessdate=2013-08-29}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |{{NGA}}\n|[[Eagle]]<br />\n|Accipitridae\n|[[File:Martial eagle (Polemaetus bellicosus).jpg|150x150px]]\n|<ref name=\":0\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.worldatlas.com/webimage/countrys/africa/nigeria/ngsymbols.htm|title=Nigeria State Symbols, Song, Flags and More - Worldatlas.com|website=www.worldatlas.com|access-date=2019-02-02}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Black crowned crane|Black Crowned Crane]] ''(national bird)''\n|''Balearica pavonina''\n|[[File:Balearica_pavonina_-_Maroparque_01.jpg|150px]]\n|<ref name=\":0\" />\n|-\n|{{PRK}}||[[Chollima]]|| style=\"background:#ccc;\" |'''Mythical'''||[[File:Chollima statue 05.JPG|150px]]||<ref>{{cite web|last=Leftley|first=Nick|title=6 Worst National Animals|url=http://www.maxim.com/travel/the-6-worst-national-animals|accessdate=8 January 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The National Animal Of North Korea Is A Chollima (Like a Pegasus)|url=http://www.unrealfacts.com/the-national-animal-of-north-korea-is-a-chollima-like-a-pegasus/|work=Unreal Facts|accessdate=8 January 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108025103/http://www.unrealfacts.com/the-national-animal-of-north-korea-is-a-chollima-like-a-pegasus/|archive-date=2014-01-08|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://abcnews.go.com/Lifestyle/national-animals-legendary-extinct-imaginary/story?id=20170452#2 |title=National Animals: The Legendary, Extinct and Imaginary-6 of 9 |publisher=abcnews.go.com |accessdate=2014-10-03}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |{{flag|Norway}}||[[Lion]] ''(royal national animal)''||''Panthera leo''||[[File:Coat of arms of Norway.svg|150px]]||<ref>{{Cite web|title = Riksv\u00e5penet er mer hellig enn flagget|url = http://www.aftenposten.no/fakta/innsikt/Riksvapenet-er-mer-hellig-enn-flagget-7926177.html|website = www.aftenposten.no|accessdate = 2015-12-27}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[White-throated dipper]] ''(national bird)''||''Cinclus cinclus''||[[File:Cinclus cinclus R(ThKraft).jpg|150px]]||<ref>{{Cite web|title = Nasjonalfugl|url = https://snl.no/nasjonalfugl|website = www.snl.no|accessdate = 2015-12-27}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Fjord horse]] ''(national horse)''||''Equus ferus caballus''||[[File:Fjording, mother and daughter.jpg|150px]]||<ref>{{Cite web|title = Fjordingene p\u00e5 Langedrag|url = http://www.langedrag.no/dyrene/hest|website = www.langedrag.no|accessdate = 2015-12-27|url-status = dead|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160105220549/http://www.langedrag.no/dyrene/hest|archivedate = 5 January 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{flag|Oman}}||[[Arabian oryx]] ''(national animal)''||''Oryx leucoryx''||[[File:Arabian oryx (oryx leucoryx).jpg|150px]]||<ref>{{Cite web|title = Oman Flag, Oman Map, Oman Culture : SphereInfo.com|url = http://www.sphereinfo.c